### Arquivo para testar as rotas da API
### Use com Thunder Client, REST Client ou Postman

### 1. Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "meuusername",
  "name": "Meu Nome Completo"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Registrar segundo usuário para testes
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario2@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "usuario2",
  "name": "Segundo Usuário"
}

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE PERFIL (REQUER AUTENTICAÇÃO)
### ========================================

### 4. Obter meu perfil
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 5. Atualizar meu perfil
PUT http://localhost:3000/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nome Atualizado",
  "bio": "Minha nova bio incrível!",
  "avatar": "https://exemplo.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### 6. Buscar perfil por username
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/meuusername
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 7. Buscar perfis (busca)
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/search?q=usuario&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========================================
### COMANDOS CURL ALTERNATIVOS
### ========================================

### Registrar usuário via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"test@test.com","password":"123456","username":"testuser","name":"Test User"}'

### Login via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"test@test.com","password":"123456"}'

### Obter perfil via curl (substitua TOKEN):
# curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/profile/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI"

### Atualizar perfil via curl:
# curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/profile/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"Novo Nome","bio":"Nova bio"}'